p.$: Abstract ANTI-IL-23P19 ANTIBODIES The present invention relates to anti-IL-23p 19 binding compounds, in particular new humanized anti IL-23p 19 antibodies, pharmaceutical compositions and therapeutic and diagnostic methods and compositions for using the same.
